                <note rend="inline" type="source">841.79658/66: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-01-13T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >January 13, 1944—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>61. Without jeopardizing possibility of favorable action by Swedish Government,
                    please endeavor to expedite final decision on subject matter of your 23, January
                    4.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
